1
00:01:01,399 --> 00:01:03,079
September 14th.

2
00:01:04,439 --> 00:01:05,760
Please book two rooms for me.

3
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,079
Today is Jiang Yue's birthday.

4
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,480
Hello.

5
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,760
Is the cake ready?

6
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,159
Yes.

7
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:25,680
Here you are.

8
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:26,799
Thank you.

9
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,560
Yue'er.

10
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,960
This is your mom's favorite necklace.

11
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,520
Keep it for me, okay?

12
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,960
[The painting in the necklace my mother left me]

13
00:02:24,159 --> 00:02:25,240
[seems to have a similar totem.]

14
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:02,960
Mom.

15
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,479
Young Master, let's go home.

16
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:05,680
Mom.

17
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,000
Take him away.

18
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:07,599
Yes.

19
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:11,759
Young Master, be good. Let's go.

20
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:13,199
Mom.

21
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,479
District 45 has always been isolated.

22
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:31,919
I'm worried

23
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,159
even if you send the young master in person,

24
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:35,919
they won't cooperate with us.

25
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,120
How did it go?

26
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:41,599
Very well.

27
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:47,400
Good.

28
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,000
You can go now.

29
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,280
Here is a guest list.

30
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,080
Only by sharing this list can we protect ourselves.

31
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,759
Who is the trading partner today?

32
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:06,919
Your task

33
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:08,639
is to ensure that each mission is completed successfully.

34
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:10,360
Don't ask what you shouldn't ask.

35
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,360
It's the anniversary of my mother's death.

36
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,280
Go to the grave with me.

37
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,199
You haven't been there for several years.

38
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,160
I don't have time today.

39
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,560
I'll fly to Duke County tomorrow morning.

40
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:24,279
Do you remember what she looks like?

41
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,399
You actually have the nerve to mention your mother to me.

42
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,879
Look how busy I am now.

43
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,879
If you could help me a bit,

44
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:36,160
would I be this busy?

45
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:41,120
Since you were a child,

46
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,920
you said you were not interested in the group's affairs,

47
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,519
and were determined to avenge your mother. Okay.

48
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,800
I thought you were a dutiful son.

49
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,079
But now?

50
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,600
Black Snow is still alive.

51
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,240
He is still eyeing us

52
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:58,839
covetously.

53
00:04:58,959 --> 00:04:59,720
What have you done?

54
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:03,800
Your mother has been dead for 16 years.

55
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:06,360
16 years.

56
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:08,000
Tell me,

57
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,519
how are you going to meet your mother?

58
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,160
Get out.

59
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,600
Jiang Yue.

60
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,959
Jiang Yue, it's me.

61
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,480
Jiang Yue.

62
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,600
[Sorry, the number you dialed is powered off.]

63
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,160
Qi Qi.

64
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:31,120
Uncle.

65
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,240
Why are you up so late?

66
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,399
Do you know where Jiang Yue went?

67
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,160
What do you need him for?

68
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,480
He didn't answer my calls

69
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,800
or reply to my messages.

70
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:42,639
It's nothing.

71
00:06:43,279 --> 00:06:44,399
He'll come back when he should.

72
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:45,639
Uncle.

73
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,759
Today is his birthday.

74
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,240
He doesn't celebrate his birthday.

75
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:53,480
Why?

76
00:06:54,959 --> 00:06:55,639
Have a good rest.

77
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,279
Mr. Gao,

78
00:07:14,839 --> 00:07:15,639
why are you here?

79
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:19,439
I'm worried about the young master.

80
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:21,639
Do you know where Jiang Yue is?

81
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,600
Qingci Cemetery.

82
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,160
Cemetery?

83
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,319
Today

84
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,560
is also the death anniversary of his mother.

85
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:44,800
April 5th,

86
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,959
1977.

87
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,639
September 14th,

88
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,959
2009.

89
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:07,480
Mom,

90
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,240
it's been 16 years.

91
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:16,639
I'm tired,

92
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:21,120
but I won't give up.

93
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,360
I will find out

94
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,480
who

95
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,559
hurt you.

96
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:39,639
Jiang Yue.

97
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:40,799
Jiang Yue.

98
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,399
Why don't you answer the phone?

99
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,600
Qi.

100
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,559
You'll make auntie sad like this.

101
00:08:50,159 --> 00:08:51,440
How do you know I'm here?

102
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:53,080
I'm worried about you.

103
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,480
Let's go home, okay?

104
00:08:55,799 --> 00:08:56,159
Go.

105
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:00,799
Come on.

106
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,279
Go.

107
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,039
Sit.

108
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,679
I'm sorry.

109
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,120
I didn't know today was...

110
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,360
I'll take it away now.

111
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,679
It's okay. I'll eat it tomorrow.

112
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:32,639
It won't be wasted.

113
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:35,919
I want to eat it.

114
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:37,799
Really?

115
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:39,639
Wait a minute.

116
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,679
Look.

117
00:09:53,519 --> 00:09:54,720
Do you have a lighter?

118
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,120
Okay.

119
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,399
Now it's time to make a wish.

120
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:10,000
Let's welcome our little birthday star Jiang Yue to make a wish.

121
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,720
Make a wish.

122
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:23,360
I haven't thought of what to wish for.

123
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,480
Then I'll make one for you.

124
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:31,919
Wish Jiang Yue...

125
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:45,480
Three,

126
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:46,519
two,

127
00:10:47,279 --> 00:10:47,799
one.

128
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:00,320
Let's cut the cake.

129
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:01,960
How should we cut it?
